PN,44301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772037602
OL,3,CResponse to child exploitation in NI
OL,4,C'inconsistent and sometimes inadequate'
OL,6,FThere is an "inconsistent" and at
OL,7,Ftimes "inadequate" criminal justice
OL,8,Fsystem response to child criminal
OL,9,Fexploitation in Northern Ireland, a
OL,10,Freport has found.
OL,12,FCriminal Justice Inspection Northern
OL,13,FIreland chief inspector Jacqui Durkin
OL,14,Fdescribed child criminal exploitation
OL,15,F(CCE) as an issue of "increasing
OL,16,Fconcern".
OL,26,@nD@MOUnD@ZO]oD@GOUoD@RO]wD@VOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772037602
OL,3,CResponse to child exploitation in NI
OL,4,C'inconsistent and sometimes inadequate'
OL,6,FShe said criminally exploited children
OL,7,Fcan be targeted by paramilitaries and
OL,8,Forganised crime gangs, going missing
OL,9,Ffrom being in care, and urged that
OL,10,Fmore is done to protect them, and to
OL,11,Funderstand the scale of the
OL,12,Fexploitation.
OL,14,FCriminal Justice Inspection inspectors
OL,15,Ffound that Northern Ireland's criminal
OL,16,Fjustice system faced significant
OL,17,Fchallenges in recognising, assessing
OL,18,Fand responding to child criminal
OL,19,Fexploitation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772037602
OL,3,CResponse to child exploitation in NI
OL,4,C'inconsistent and sometimes inadequate'
OL,6,FThey acknowledged the difficult work
OL,7,Fundertaken on a daily basis by police
OL,8,Fofficers to help children in complex
OL,9,Fand challenging circumstances, and
OL,10,Fconcern was raised around their
OL,11,Fresourcing.
OL,13,FHowever inspectors found the PSNI did
OL,14,Fnot have a clear model in place for
OL,15,Ftackling child criminal exploitation
OL,16,Facross the organisation, and that
OL,17,Ffrontline officers and staff lacked
OL,18,Fawareness and training on child
OL,19,Fcriminal exploitation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772037602
OL,3,CResponse to child exploitation in NI
OL,4,C'inconsistent and sometimes inadequate'
OL,6,FCase file reviews carried out as part
OL,7,Fof inspection fieldwork found children
OL,8,Fwere "often treated as suspects rather
OL,9,Fthan victims and safeguarding
OL,10,Freferrals were not always made in a
OL,11,Ftimely manner".
OL,13,FInspectors also found evidence of
OL,14,Fvictim-blaming language in some
OL,15,Frecords they examined during
OL,16,Ffieldwork, and a lack of specific
OL,17,Fmarkers on PSNI or Public Prosecution
OL,18,FService for Northern Ireland case
OL,19,Frecord computer systems.
OL,21,FThey made four recommendations.
OL,26,@pD@FOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772037602
OL,3,CResponse to child exploitation in NI
OL,4,C'inconsistent and sometimes inadequate'
OL,6,FThese include the Department of
OL,7,FJustice working in collaboration with
OL,8,Fcriminal justice organisations to
OL,9,Fdevelop a strategic framework, and
OL,10,Fthat the PSNI immediately develop an
OL,11,Fadequately resourced delivery model
OL,12,Ffor the identification, response and
OL,13,Fdisruption of child criminal
OL,14,Fexploitation across the organisation.
OL,16,FMs Durkin said the report "makes for
OL,17,Fconcerning reading".
OL,26,@xD@[OUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772037602
OL,3,CResponse to child exploitation in NI
OL,4,C'inconsistent and sometimes inadequate'
OL,6,FShe said: "While pockets of good
OL,7,Fpractice including the use of multi-
OL,8,Fagency support hubs and targeted
OL,9,Finterventions were identified, based
OL,10,Fon the evidence gathered and
OL,11,Fconsidered during this inspection,
OL,12,Finspectors concluded outcomes for
OL,13,Fchildren who had experienced or were
OL,14,Fat risk of child criminal exploitation
OL,15,Fwere not good.
OL,17,F"The challenge for the criminal
OL,18,Fjustice system and others is to
OL,19,Fimplement the two strategic and two
OL,20,Foperational recommendations for
OL,21,Fimprovement included in this report.
OL,26,@nD@KOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772037602
OL,3,CResponse to child exploitation in NI
OL,4,C'inconsistent and sometimes inadequate'
OL,6,F"We need to see children as children,
OL,7,Fprotect them from harm and vigorously
OL,8,Fpursue those who are exploiting them
OL,9,Fand robbing them of their childhood.
OL,11,F"This is not a drama storyline ` this
OL,12,Fis the work of all of us and there is
OL,13,Fno time to waste."
OL,15,FJustice Minister Naomi Long responded
OL,16,Fsaying the report "provides important
OL,17,Fand timely insights into how the
OL,18,Fjustice system can better recognise,
OL,19,Fprevent and respond".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@RO]xD@SOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772037602
OL,3,CResponse to child exploitation in NI
OL,4,C'inconsistent and sometimes inadequate'
OL,6,FShe added: "My department accepts the
OL,7,Frecommendations and is in the process
OL,8,Fof working with partner organisations
OL,9,Fto establish a child-centred child
OL,10,Fexploitation strategic framework for
OL,11,Fjustice outcomes."
OL,13,FDetective Chief Superintendent Zoe
OL,14,FMcKee said the PSNI acknowledges the
OL,15,Ffindings and recommendations made by
OL,16,FCriminal Justice Inspection.
OL,26,@nD@LOUsD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772037602
OL,3,CResponse to child exploitation in NI
OL,4,C'inconsistent and sometimes inadequate'
OL,6,FShe said: "Alongside the Department of
OL,7,FJustice and other key partners, we are
OL,8,Flaser-focused in tackling child
OL,9,Fcriminal exploitation, an issue that
OL,10,Frequires a whole system approach.
OL,12,F"Significant work to tackle CCE is
OL,13,Falready under way.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772037602
OL,3,CResponse to child exploitation in NI
OL,4,C'inconsistent and sometimes inadequate'
OL,6,F"We have established enhanced
OL,7,Fgovernance arrangements to drive
OL,8,Fdelivery of shared objectives through
OL,9,Fa cross-departmental action plan,
OL,10,Freporting through our established CCE
OL,11,FDelivery Group led by senior
OL,12,Fleadership within Public Protection
OL,13,FBranch."
OL,15,FShe added other work is under way,
OL,16,Fwhile training and awareness are also
OL,17,Fbeing strengthened, and an
OL,18,Forganisation-wide e-learning package
OL,19,Fis under development.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
