OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772037602
OL,3,CResponse to child exploitation in NI
OL,4,C'inconsistent and sometimes inadequate'
OL,6,FMs McKee said: "I also acknowledge the
OL,7,Freport's observations regarding
OL,8,Fresourcing.
OL,10,F"Despite ongoing financial and
OL,11,Fworkforce constraints, our specialist
OL,12,Fofficers and staff in Public
OL,13,FProtection Branch and across local
OL,14,Fpolicing continue to work hard to
OL,15,Fbetter protect some of the most
OL,16,Fvulnerable children in our society."
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
